tetris.pieces

Interface ImmutablePiece

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Piece
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPiece, IPiece, JPiece, LPiece, OPiece, SPiece, TPiece, ZPiece

    public interface ImmutablePiece
    This interface defines the required operations of immutable Tetris pieces. Your pieces will implement either this interface or the MutablePiece interface, but not both.
    Version:
    Autumn 2012
    Author:
    Daniel M. Zimmerman
